      "rationale": "A large-deformation elastoplastic formulation with surface-to-surface contact (penalty method, friction coefficient 0.2) was selected based on literature precedent for metallic spinal implant FEA. Sensitivity to friction coefficient and plasticity hardening parameters was evaluated. The model form is consistent with ASTM F1717 loading regime. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
