      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V ELI) material properties (elastic modulus, yield strength, hardening curve) were obtained from coupon tensile tests on material from the same lot as the test constructs. Geometric dimensions were measured via CMM on three representative screws. Input uncertainty propagated through Latin hypercube sampling (n=200 runs). Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
