      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All specimens were production-equivalent hardware with documented lot traceability. Inter-laboratory variability assessed; coefficient of variation < 8% for all QoIs. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
