      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single ASTM F1717 standard condition (5 mm offset, room temperature, quasi-static loading rate). While this condition is clinically representative, only one load configuration was evaluated. A bounding argument is provided but not experimentally verified across additional configurations. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3, representing a known gap acknowledged in the submission."
