    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 is accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors were assessed; eleven achieved their required levels. The Test conditions factor achieved level 2 against a required level 3, which is acknowledged as a gap with a bounding argument provided. The Relevance of the validation activities to the COU factor was not assessed and was considered beyond scope without a concrete alternative justification — this gap is noted but deemed acceptable given the direct correspondence between ASTM F1717 test conditions and the COU loading regime. The overall E/uval metric is satisfied for all primary QoIs across three independent FEA codes and N=11 experimental specimens.",
